<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MYPD 마이데이터의 첫걸음</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/home.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/default.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/logo-fabicon.png">
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navigation">
        <div class="top">
            <div class="menu_left">
                <h1><a href="/main"><img src = "../images/logo.png" width="230px" height="100%" alt="MYPD" class="logo"></a></h1>
                <ul id="main-menu">
                    <li class="menu_list"><a href="/main#scroll_about">About</a></li>
                    <% if(isAuthenticated){ %>
                        <li><div class="menu_list"><a href="">Mypage</a></div>
                            <ul id="sub-menu">
                                <div class="sub_menu_box">
                                    <li><a href="/mypage/reg_svc_list" aria-label="subemnu"  class="sub_list">테스트 관리</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="/mypage/editcheck" aria-label="subemnu"  class="sub_list">회원정보 수정</a></li>
                                </div>  
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <% } %>
                        <li class="menu_list" style="margin-right: 40px;"><a href="/main#scroll_contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="menu">
                <% if(isAuthenticated){ %>
                    <li id="logout_btn"><p><%= currentUser.nickname %>님</p></li>
                    <li id="logout_btn"><p> | </p></li>
                    <li id="logout_btn"><a href="/user/logout" style="margin-top: 5px;">로그아웃</a></li>

                <% } else { %>
                    <a class="login_box" href="/user/login" >로그인</a>
                <% } %> 
    
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="city_short">
        <div> 
            <!-- 메인 첫 소개 -->
                <div class="testbed_main_first">
                    <h1><span style="font-weight:700; color:black;">mypd 기업용 테스트베드로<br>개발과 테스트를 편리하게</h1>
                    <h3>mypd에서는 기업사용자에게 세가지 테스트를 지원해요</h3>
                </div>
               
            <!-- 메인소개 끝 -->
        </div>

        <div class="testbed-box">
            <div class="test-wrap">
                <div class="test-box">
                    <div class="test-box-title"><div>마이데이터<br>서비스 테스트</div></div>
                    <div class="test-box-line"></div>
                    <div class="test-box-pic1"></div>
                    <div class="test-box-content">여러분의 마이데이터 서비스를<br>테스트해보세요.</div>
                    <div class="test-box-button">
                        <a href="/testbed/unit_svc">단위테스트</a>
                        <a href="/testbed/inte_svc">통합테스트</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="test-box">
                    <div class="test-box-title"><div>API 서버 테스트</div></div>
                    <div class="test-box-line"></div>
                    <div class="test-box-pic2"></div>
                    <div class="test-box-content">여러분의 API서버를<br>테스트해보세요.</div>
                    <div class="test-box-button">
                        <a href="/testbed/unit_api">단위테스트</a>
                        <a href="/testbed/inte_api">통합테스트</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="test-box">
                    <div class="test-box-title"><div>연동 테스트</div></div>
                    <div class="test-box-line"></div>
                    <div class="test-box-pic3"></div>
                    <div class="test-box-content">여러분의 서비스와<br>다른 사용자의 서비스를 연동해보세요.</div>
                    <div class="test-box-button">
                        <a href="/testbed/link_svc">서비스 테스트</a>
                        <a href="/testbed/link_api">API 테스트</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
